    "We also consider all trainers in our toolkit including: (1) supervised fine-tuning, denoted as SFT; (2) supervised fine-tuning with a frozen retriever, denoted as SwR; and (3) fusion-in-decoder training, denoted as FiD.",
    "Since LOCALRQA features developing new RQA systems locally, we compare against the most powerful models accessible remotely.",
    "This include using text-ada-002 (OpenAI, 2022a) as the retriever, and prompting GPT-3.5-turbo (ChatGPT) and GPT-4-turbo as the generative models.",
